






The Ministry of Youth Affairs and Sports has cleared the 
proposals worth over Rs. 142.24 crore for providing Grant-in-Aid to fourteen 
States for creation of basic sports infrastructure in 12854 village panchayats 
and 376 block panchayats under Panchayat Yuva Krida Aur Khel Abhiyan (PYKKA) 
during the year 2008-2009. The details of the proposals are as follows: 
 
